<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Podcast Episode</title>

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #111;
      background: #fff;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      background: #0b0b0b;
      color: white;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .episode {
      color: #f97316;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .subtitle {
      color: #ccc;
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      background: #f97316;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* SECTIONS */
    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* LAYOUT */
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    /* BOXES */
    .box {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Timestamps */
    .timestamp {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }

    /* Sidebar */
    .sidebar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 20px;
    }

    a {
      color: #f97316;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    .footer {
      background: #f3f3f3;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    input {
      padding: 10px;
      width: 80%;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    button {
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: black;
      color: white;
      border: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="episode">Episode 1412</div>

    <h1>
      The Skin Mistakes That Age You Fast and Kill You Slow
    </h1>

    <div class="subtitle">
      Skin cancer prevention, anti-aging strategies and modern dermatology insights.
    </div>

    <a class="btn" href="#listen">▶ Listen Now</a>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- AUDIO -->
<section id="listen">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Listen</h2>

    <audio controls style="width:100%;">
      <source src="your-audio-file.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
    </audio>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MAIN -->
<section>
  <div class="container grid">

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <div>

      <h2>Episode Summary</h2>
      <p>
        In this episode we explore skin cancer prevention, early detection techniques,
        sunscreen myths and modern anti-aging dermatology approaches.
      </p>

      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Melanoma is often misdiagnosed early</li>
        <li>Sun exposure is not the only risk factor</li>
        <li>Dermoscopy improves detection accuracy</li>
        <li>Retinoids have strong anti-aging effects</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Timestamps</h2>

      <div class="timestamp"><span>00:00</span><span>Intro</span></div>
      <div class="timestamp"><span>01:40</span><span>Guest Intro</span></div>
      <div class="timestamp"><span>12:30</span><span>Skin Cancer Basics</span></div>
      <div class="timestamp"><span>25:10</span><span>Treatment Options</span></div>

      <h2>Transcript</h2>
      <p>
        Host: Welcome to the show...<br><br>
        Guest: Thank you for having me...
      </p>

    </div>

    <!-- SIDEBAR -->
    <div class="sidebar">

      <div class="box">
        <h3>Resources</h3>
        <p><a href="#">Guest Website</a></p>
        <p><a href="#">Research Papers</a></p>
        <p><a href="#">Book Mentioned</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="box">
        <h3>About Guest</h3>
        <p>
          Dermatology expert focused on early melanoma detection and skin health optimization.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
  <h2>Get Updates</h2>
  <p>Subscribe to new episodes</p>

  <input type="email" placeholder="Your email"/>
  <br/>
  <button>Subscribe</button>
</div>

</body>
</html>
